                               'Webly' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Webly' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to connect all
octagonal shaped tiles on each game board. To connect tiles, just
click on a tile and the game will randomly create a link between
it and another tile that is located nearby. If a link was already
present between both tiles, that link will change its colour...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves...

  Have fun!

